{
  "texts": [
    "We considered advancing AIMS projects to additional validation studies based on the ability to reorder at least some of the initial SD hits, the availability of chemical analogs in the screening library to the initial hits, the capability to perform dose-response experiments, and the ability of the collaborators to perform additional screens and return results promptly.",
    "We performed two sets of experiments: DR validation of the SD hits from AIMS and analoging with DR readouts.",
    "We performed DR measurements using the same assays and protocols as SD.",
    "We performed an analoging round by identifying, for each AIMS hit, its 1000 nearest neighbors from the Mcule library 76, using molecular fingerprints similarity 68.",
    "We augmented the set with additional analogs using substructure 83 or FTrees 84 searches, if needed."
  ]
}